      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i feel like i don't even exist lol. i work from this tiny apartment all day, stare at a screen, send emails, and then close the laptop. if i just didn't log on tomorrow or something... i don't even think anyone would notice the difference. it's like i'm just a ghost in a machine.",
